author: Dan Taekema
title: First Ontario-made medical masks ready for use, says premier
description: Ontario-made medical masks are rolling of the line at a GTA auto parts manufacturer thanks in part to engineers at McMaster University and Premier Doug Ford was on hand Tuesday to pick up the first load.
content:
Ontario-made medical masks are rolling of the line at a GTA auto parts manufacturer thanks in part to engineers at McMaster University.
